OL,3,CUber driver shot and killed by Ohio
OL,4,Cman after scam callers targeted them
OL,5,Cboth
OL,7,FAn Ohio man who police say killed an
OL,8,FUber driver he thought was trying to
OL,9,Frob him after they were both duped by
OL,10,Fscammers has been charged with murder.
OL,12,FWilliam Brock, 81, also faces charges
OL,13,Fof kidnapping and felonious assault,
OL,14,Fwhich he denies.
OL,16,FThe shooting took place on March 25 at
OL,17,FBrock's home in South Charleston,
OL,18,FClark County, Ohio.
