OL,7,FOfficers from the sheriff's office
OL,8,Fresponded after Brock called 911 and
OL,9,Fsaid he had shot someone who was
OL,10,Ftrying to rob him.
OL,12,FBrock had received scam calls from
OL,13,Fsomeone pretending to be an officer
OL,14,Ffrom the local court who eventually
OL,15,Fbegan making threats and demanding
OL,16,Fmoney, authorities said.
