OL,3,CUber driver shot and killed by Ohio
OL,4,Cman after scam callers targeted them
OL,5,Cboth
OL,7,FThe victim, Loletha Hall, 61, was an
OL,8,FUber driver who had been told to
OL,9,Fretrieve a package from Brock's home,
OL,10,Fa request authorities say was possibly
OL,11,Fmade by the same scam caller or an
OL,12,Faccomplice.
OL,14,FHall had no knowledge of the calls
OL,15,Fmade to Brock, authorities said.
OL,17,FWhen she arrived at the home and got
OL,18,Fout of her car, Brock pulled out a gun
OL,19,Fand demanded she tell him who had made
OL,20,Fthe threatening calls.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/6
