OL,5,Cboth
OL,7,FHe also took Hall's cellphone and
OL,8,Fwould not let her leave.
OL,10,FWhen Hall tried to get away, Brock
OL,11,Fshot her once, police said, then shot
OL,12,Fher two more times as they discussed
OL,13,Fthe situation.
OL,15,FBrock somehow sustained a minor head
OL,16,Finjury during the confrontation and he
OL,17,Fcalled 911 shortly after he fired the
OL,18,Fthird shot.
OL,20,FHall was taken to a hospital but later
OL,21,Fdied there from her wounds.
