OL,7,FBrock initially was charged with
OL,8,Fmurder because authorities said Hall
OL,9,Fdid not pose an active threat when she
OL,10,Fwas shot. His next court hearing is
OL,11,Fscheduled on Monday.
OL,13,FThe original scam calls to Brock and
OL,14,FHall remain under investigation,
OL,15,Fpolice said, and it's not clear yet if
OL,16,Fthe calls were placed by the same
OL,17,Fperson.
